s to the process of moving money from one bank account to another. This can be done through various means, including online banking, mobile banking apps, wire transfers,  Bank fund transfer refers to the process of moving money from one bank account to another.\",\"left_img\":\"global\\/images\\/6WNNQQuh1wsN94HrO2xX.png\",\"left_shape_img\":\"global\\/images\\/04C4SrC8P2fi2eXDpVYA.png\",\"mask_shape_img\":\"global\\/images\\/pJKbUFqIorpzdmi8H0mJ.png\"}',1,'2022-10-22 13:54:48','2024-06-07 06:26:56',4,'en'),(11,'Video Section\n','videosection','{\"small_title\":\"Bank Introduction\",\"big_title\":\"Know The digi Bank\",\"video_link\":\"https:\\/\\/youtu.be\\/9341cn0KokE\",\"thumbnail_img\":\"global\\/images\\/xpspOSoJaTqw1YvwglJd.jpg\",\"left_shape_img\":\"global\\/images\\/bB8WRVsqjXx0f18mObW1.png\"}',1,'2022-10-22 13:54:48','2024-06-12 12:23:40',9,'en'),(12,'Experience Section\r\n','experiencesection','{\"title_small\":\"Tailored experiences\",\"title_big\":\"Our Powerful Solutions\",\"description\":\"Fund transfer involves moving money from one account to another, whether it\'s within the same financial institution or between different banks. This process can be initiated through various channels, including online banking, mobile banking apps, ATM transactions, wire transfers, or in-person visits to bank branches.\",\"left_img\":\"global\\/images\\/ooVxFs7wZj2KVGptmPpR.png\",\"left_shape_img\":\"global\\/images\\/04C4SrC8P2fi2eXDpVYA.png\",\"right_img\":\"global\\/images\\/x1AJhPJgfB30mkoLjiG7.png\"}',1,'2022-10-22 13:54:48','2024-06-10 06:27:30',7,'en'),(13,'Testimonial Section\r\n','testimonialsection','{\"title_small\":\"Testimonials\",\"title_big\":\"Trustworthy Feedback From Our Customers\"}',1,'2022-10-22 13:54:48','2024-06-07 06:26:56',10,'en'),(62,'Work Step Section\r\n','workstepsection','[]',1,'2022-10-22 07:54:48','2024-06-07 00:26:56',3,'en'),(97,'Loan Calculator Section\r\n','loancalculatorsection','{\"title_small\":\"Loan Calculator\",\"title_big\":\